        ["The door was opened quietly while everyone was still asleep.", "دروازہ خاموشی سے کھولا گیا جب سب سو رہے تھے", "darwaza khamoshi se khola gaya jab sab so rahe the"],
        ["Mistakes were found in the first draft, so we rewrote it.", "پہلے مسودے میں غلطیاں ملیں اس لیے ہم نے دوبارہ لکھا", "pehle musawwade mein ghaltiyaan milein is liye hum ne dobara likha"],
